{"tid":2325230,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"超越神隱少女！《鬼滅之刃》59天賣破300億日圓創紀錄","createTime":"2020-12-14T12:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T14:50:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf680e5384f7d8a894017747d47cc43549ed258","tid":2325230,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:26:09.000Z","msg":"日本人氣動漫「鬼滅之刃」改編的動畫電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》，在上映後創下票房奇蹟，目前票房累積達到302億8930萬7700日圓（約新台幣82.8億元），僅69天就突破了300億日圓票房，改寫了《神隱少女》當初累積的253天紀錄，成為最快達成300億日圓票房的電影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/08/2869094-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F08%2F2869094-PH.jpg&h=a2335dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼《鬼滅之刃劇場版：無限列車篇》成為最快達成300億日圓票房的電影。（圖／木棉花提供）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/01/2856705-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2F2856705-PH.jpg&h=1acdfda4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據日本放送協會（NHK）報導指出，《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》從10月16日上映以來至12月13日為止，共累積了2253萬9385人進電影院觀賞、302億8930萬7700日圓的票房，離冠軍《神隱少女》的308億日元票房僅差不到6億元，有機會在下周就超越《神隱少女》成為日本影史票房冠軍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/30/2801050-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F2801050-PH.jpg&h=827b35a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本影史賣座冠軍《神隱少女》的308億日圓票房即將被超越。（圖／甲上提供）<br />\n<br />\n但其實，在《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》票房即將超越《神隱少女》之際，許多的日本網友卻難以接受這樣的事實，更直呼：「其實知道《鬼滅之刃》很厲害，但看到《神隱少女》被超越，不知道為什麼總覺得有點感傷。」"},{"pid":"476b19f50b8deac17e0907b51f5c71b99d2e71e5","tid":2325230,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:27:16.000Z","msg":"有冇計通脹先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703676551154cbb9caf910f3585f547aa4ecc127","tid":2325230,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzdhmxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwzdhmxF.jpg&h=1b64b292&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f34aaeb95df7e596d992a6fa4c0a33c9a3152b0","tid":2325230,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會太癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8067385e39095dfc2e9a06d5d0416816b6f97a9a","tid":2325230,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f34aaeb95df7e596d992a6fa4c0a33c9a3152b0","tid":2325230,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會太癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:32:06.000Z","msg":"鬼知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0492bd24cd258584f4bb92cfc9ad9150a972f0","tid":2325230,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703676551154cbb9caf910f3585f547aa4ecc127","tid":2325230,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply